 Limit Pod resources
 ====================
 containers:
  - name: sise
    image: image:tag
    ports:
    - containerPort: port
    resources:
      limits:
        memory: "64Mi"
        cpu: "50m"
        
======
Debug the pod

kubectl describe po pod_name
kubectl get events

=========

Diff the declarative Objects -

 kubectl diff -f kube_object
 ==========
 
 Pod States - Pending, Running, Succeeded, Failed, Unkown
